snippet.textDisplay:
So this Qawali was sung together by their ancestors (Ustad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan and Amjad Sabri's father and uncle_Sabri Brothers) way back many years (almost 50 yrs back) in Karachi. Now their children's continue their legacy and sung it together. This on was memorable for both of them and to us too.
Sad thing is, Amjad Sabri left us before release of this Qawali.

Maati ke tum deeware
jo sunyo hamri baat,
aaj milaawara mohe piya ka
jo jagyo saari raat.

Aaj rang hai ri maan
rang hai ri,
more khaajah ke ghar rang hai ri,

aaj sajan milaawara more aangan mein
sajan milaawara more aangan mein,

aaj rang hai ri maan
rang hai ri.

raini charhi rasool ki
so rang maula ke haath
jis ki choonar rang diyo
so dhan dhan wa ke bhaag,

aaj rang hai ae maan
rang hai ri,
mere

mere mahboob ke ghar
ae ri sakhi re mere mahboob ke ghar,
rang hai ree
aaj rang hai ae maan rang hai ree .

Mohe peer paayo nijaam ud-deen auliya,
nijaam ud-deen auliya
ala ud-deen auliya

main to jab dekhoon more sang hai ri maan rang hai ri
aaj rang hai e maan
rang hai ri.

des vides men dhoond phiri hoon,
tora rang man bhaayo nijaam ud-deen,
tora rang man bhaayo main tora rang,

bhul rahi re maan
main to aiso rang
mahboob-e ilaahi
main to aiso rang
mahboob-e ilaahi.

khusro rain suhaag ki so main jaagi pi ke sang,
tan mora man peehu ka,
so donon ek hi rang
main to aiso rang
mahboob-e ilaahi
main to aiso rang.

gokul dekha
mathura dekha,

poorab dekha
pashchhim dekha,

uttar dekha
dakkhan dekha,
par tosa na koi rang dekha
par tosa nah koyi rang dekha re.

Main to aiso rang
mahboob-i ilaahi .

phiri zamaane men chaar jaanib
allah
nigaar-i yakta tumheen ko dekha
haseen dekhe jameel dekhe
bas ek tum sa tumheen ko dekha

main to aiso rang
mahboob-i ilaahi,
main to aiso rang.

Des bides men dhoond phiri hoon,
mohe tora rang man bhaayo nijaam ud-deen
tora rang man bhaayo nijaam ud-deen.

Jag jag jag jag
jag jag jag ujyaaro
jag ujyaaro
jag ujyaaro,

khaajah nijaam ud-deen jagat ujyaaro
saabir 'ala ud-deen jagat ujyaaro .

Meharwa
meharwa ras boondaan barse,
boondan barse ras boondan barse,

khaajagaan ke darbaaran men,
aaj dekho ghan garje,
ras boondaan barse
meharwa ras boondaan barse .

Khaajah fareed ud-deen auliya
qutub ud-deen auliya,

khaajah mu'een ud-deen auliya
khaajah qutub ud-deen auliya,

khaajah nijaam ud-deen
khaajah naseer ud-deen
khaajah nijaam ud-deen
khaajah naseer ud-deen.

Aaj shuhrah nijaam naseer ud-deen ka
laa'l mahboob bana (loop),
nijaam ud-deen auliya jag ujyaaro,

jagat ujyaaro,
jag ujyaaro jagat ujyaaro .

Teri soorat se kisi ki naheen milti soorat,
ham jahaan men tiri tasweer liye phirte hain
dekho main to aiso rang
mahboob-i ilaahi
main to aiso rang
mahboob-i ilaahi.

Nijaam ud-deen auliya jag ujyaaro,
jag ujyaaro jagat ujyaaro,
wuh to jo maange barsat hai ri maan rang hai ri .

Aaj rang hai ri maan
aaj rang hai ri maan.
